Package hr.fer.zemris.java.webserver.workers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BgColorWorker
    The worker updates the current background color and displays a message about the change and a link to the original page.
    CircleWorker
    Produces a png image with dimensions 200x200 and with a single filled circle.
    EchoParams
    The worker ouputs back to the user the parameters it obtained formatted as an HTML table.
    HelloWorker
    The worker creates a html page with current time displayed and gives a different message depending on the parameter "name" provided in the request.
    Home
    Displays a page with multiple links, a calculator and a background color change form that changes the client's session color.
    SumWorker
    Accepts two parameters a, b (if there are no parameters and the values cannot be parsed, then the parameters are set to default values, calculates their sum, and displays a HTML page with a table, showing a,b and the result of the operation.
